\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{G_{yy}}$
\end_inset

 is the measurement autocovariance defined as 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathbf{G_{yy}}=\mathbf{Q_{yy}}+\mathbf{HXQ_{\beta\beta}X}^{T}\mathbf{H}^{T}.
\]

\end_inset


